  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State has reasonable grounds to suspect that MERCANTILE & MARITIME GROUP is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because MERCANTILE & MARITIME GROUP is owned or controlled directly or indirectly by Murtaza Ali LAKHANI, who is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia. \n",
